123
00:07:51,568 --> 00:07:53,068
Ada apa, Rintaro?

124
00:07:53,068 --> 00:07:54,468
Yah...

125
00:07:54,468 --> 00:07:57,368
Kami minta maaf karena mengganggumu ketika kau sedang sibuk.

126
00:07:57,368 --> 00:08:00,368
Kau pasti Dewa Keberuntungan karena sejak kau datang,

127
00:08:00,368 --> 00:08:02,868
tokonya menjadi sangat sibuk.

128
00:08:02,868 --> 00:08:06,668
Aku datang ingin melihat seperti apakah telapak tangan Dewa Keberuntungan.

129
00:08:06,668 --> 00:08:08,268
Telapak tanganku?

130
00:08:08,268 --> 00:08:10,068
Oh. Tentu.

131
00:08:10,068 --> 00:08:11,868
Silahkan dan lihatlah.

132
00:08:11,868 --> 00:08:13,468
Ini...

133
00:08:14,768 --> 00:08:16,468
