140
00:08:36,568 --> 00:08:39,368
Sudah kubilang.

141
00:08:39,368 --> 00:08:41,468
Kau fantastis, Mitsuhiko.

142
00:08:43,368 --> 00:08:46,768
Sayang sekali Mitsuhiko yang mendapat pujian kali ini.

143
00:08:46,768 --> 00:08:50,268
Tapi bisakah hal seperti ini sungguh terjadi?

144
00:08:50,268 --> 00:08:51,568
Masalahnya adalah,

145
00:08:51,568 --> 00:08:54,368
